OL,3,CReform UK nominates new Sandwell
OL,4,CCouncil leader
OL,6,FRay Nock has been selected as Reform
OL,7,FUK leader on Sandwell Council.JThe
OL,8,Fparty has a majority meaning Nock will
OL,9,Fbe elected leader of the council at
OL,10,Fthe next full council meeting.
OL,12,FLabour had controlled the authority
OL,13,Fsince 1979. Reform UK took 41 seats
OL,14,Fout of a possible 72.
OL,16,FSpeaking after Reform's victory in
OL,17,FSandwell, Nock said "I want to turn
OL,18,Fthe ship. It's been going into a storm
OL,19,Fnow for 20, 30 years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
