OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778674272
OL,3,CReform UK nominates new Sandwell
OL,4,CCouncil leader
OL,6,F"We've got social deprivation issues
OL,7,Fthat are shocking. We've got health
OL,8,Fissues that are shocking. Education
OL,9,Fand housing issues that are shocking,
OL,10,Fand we've got to make a change."
OL,12,FOutgoing Labour council leader Kerry
OL,13,FCarmichael said: "It worries me what's
OL,14,Fgoing to happen, I know the people of
OL,15,FBlackheath can be quite demanding as
OL,16,Fwell.
OL,18,F"Hopefully these guys will step up and
OL,19,Fdo the right thing for these people,
OL,20,Fincluding myself because they're my
OL,21,Fcouncillors now."
